== AGENT

 Egor Zakharov, Skolkovo Institute of Science and Technology

== GOAL

Creation of 'deepfakes', or perfect realism, from paintings and images

== DATA

Datasets of facial movements from multiple people

== METHODS

Unsupervised

== RESULTS

A realistically expressive image

== ISSUES

Lacks perfect realism

== SCORE

8

== COMMENTS

If this achieves perfection it could lead to ethical issues if real can not be distinguished from fake